// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-0789 — Mass File Rename (safepay)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 28da2ffe-9078-5753-962a-2289da711916

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
